column5: Hi all,Well the ice has reached the no go point for me, did see a skidoo RIP across in front of the house 20 minutes ago, Darwin Awards contender. I have a bunch of fishing videos to make from my last outings , the very last one being 3 days ago for crappie. Was doing lots of crappie fishing as walleye was closed and was limiting the travel by staying on my home lake. Yesterday my son asked if we could do another cooking video together and so we made Fish Tacos ans filmed the process. https://youtu.be/O2bVbMHehpA
Good one!!! Keep pumpin out these videos!!

Thanks for sharing Simon! Just spent an enjoyable 30 minutes bouncing around your youtube page and watching a bunch of summer stuff to get myself pumped for this coming season (if off of lockdown) - really loved this onehttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wcp8h7ajo2Q Cheers Andrew
